INSERT INTO monumento (nombreMon, idioma, descMon) VALUES ('busto', 'en', 'In the summer of 1909, Legendre was invited by the Dominican Father Matías to visit the sanctuary of La Peña de Francia, which initially attracted him because of the connection of its name with France, due to the discovery of the image of the virgin in the sanctuary by the Frenchman Simón Vela in the Middle Ages. Two years later, accompanied by Jacques Chevalier, he wrote in the album of the sanctuary what can be considered the reason for his interest:');
INSERT INTO monumento (nombreMon, idioma, descMon) VALUES ('busto', 'en', '"With all the confidence that comes from the supplication already answered, I ask the Virgin of La Peña to allow me to return many more times to her Sanctuary, and to show the way to numerous friends from France; because it is here that Spanish and French hearts can best fraternise in Christianity."');
INSERT INTO monumento (nombreMon, idioma, descMon) VALUES ('busto', 'en', 'Maurice Legendre came to La Alberca for the first time, back in 1912, from which time every year he spent three or four months in the municipality of La Alberca and brought his friends, such as Miguel de Unamuno and Gregorio Marañón, with him. The love he felt for this town and this land meant that he made it known both through his writings and by getting people to visit the town, being one of the main promoters of the fact that La Alberca is today a National Historic-Artistic Monument and one of the Spanish tourist destinations par excellence.');
