INSERT INTO otroslugares (categoriaOtros, idioma, nombreOtro, descrOtro) VALUES ('hurdes','en','intro','In 1289, the head of the lordship relinquished part of its territory to La Alberca. The latter made the territory profitable by means of leases, which allowed the usufructuaries to make use of the land in exchange for a rent that the Albercan visitors collected annually, creating tensions and confrontations between lessors and lessees due to the heavy charges that the Hurdanos had to pay.');
INSERT INTO otroslugares (categoriaOtros, idioma, nombreOtro, descrOtro) VALUES ('hurdes','en','intro','In 1450, the lordship of Granada was donated to the lords of Valdecorneja, imposing a new exploitation regime for the whole territory. However, the authorities of La Alberca maintained their rights over the former dehesa through the collection of the census and the repartimientos until the beginning of the 19th century, when the reforms carried out by successive liberal governments initiated an ambitious programme of modernisation of the country, the result of which was the configuration of the region as an independent area and the implementation of a new system of land exploitation which, although it enshrined the "sacred right of ownership", put an end to the old privileges that La Alberca had over part of this territory.');
